paper_metadata.extraction_summary: Extracted information on the KCNH2 gene variant c.2274G>T, p.Gly925Val, including clinical significance, patient demographics, and penetrance data.

patients.phenotype: Sudden cardiac death (SCD) due to possible cardiac arrhythmia

individual_records.phenotype_details: Suffered a sudden cardiac death while attending to her child.
individual_records.evidence_sentence: Patient 1 suffered a sudden cardiac death (SCD) aged 38 years while attending to her child.

functional_data.summary: No specific functional data provided for this variant.

variants.additional_notes: The variant is of uncertain significance and was identified alongside a pathogenic FLNC variant.
key_quotes: Postmortem exome sequencing was performed in a research laboratory and identified a likely pathogenic deletion resulting in a frameshift and a premature stop codon in FLNC c.4000_4015del, p.Ala1334Profs*6, and a missense variant of uncertain significance in KCNH2 c.2274G>T, p.Gly925Val.

extraction_metadata.notes: Only one variant in KCNH2 was reported in the paper.
